                    "patching_rect": [ 15.0, 224.0, 152.0, 100.0 ],
                    "text": "Creating a new comment:\n1. Unlock the patch\n2. Type the letter 'n' (for new object)\n3. Type the word comment\n4. Hit the Return key (on a Mac, or Enter on PC)"
