                    "maxclass": "comment",
                    "numinlets": 1,
                    "numoutlets": 0,
                    "patching_rect": [ 169.0, 224.0, 152.0, 221.0 ],
                    "text": "Changing the look of a comment:\n1. Unlock the patch\n2. Select the comment\n3. Hit the 'i' button on the right side of the toolbar (alternatively, hit CMD + i (on a Mac, CTL + i on a PC))\n4. In this screen, you will find the comment object's \"attributes\" i.e., things you can change about the way it looks or behaves (these attributes only apply to this particular comment object)"
                }
            },
